  "LawName": "現役軍人進入歌劇影院等公共娛樂場所優待辦法",
  "LawURL": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?pcode=D0040013",
  "LawCategory": "行政＞內政部＞役政目",
  "LawModifiedDate": "19620123",
